Package de.dlr.proseo.ordermgr.rest.model

Klasse RestUtil

java.lang.Object
de.dlr.proseo.ordermgr.rest.model.RestUtil
@Component public class RestUtil extends Object
A utility class for converting REST jobs, job steps and parameter lists from their model equivalent.
Autor:
Ernst Melchinger
